com.kirankunigiri.Sprint.Interpolators

Class CubicInterpolator

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.animation.Interpolator
      • com.kirankunigiri.Sprint.Interpolators.EasingInterpolator
        • com.kirankunigiri.Sprint.Interpolators.CubicInterpolator

  • public class CubicInterpolator
extends EasingInterpolator
    A cubic interpolator, simply defined by f(x) = x3.

    This interpolator accelerates faster than the QuadraticInterpolator and decelerates later.

    The following curve illustrates the interpolation.

    The math in this class is taken from http://www.robertpenner.com/easing/.
